entries.journal_entry_description: It's time to go after the Trinity. Tansarii will finally be rid of the Black Sun once and for all, if you succeed.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Use the space terminal to launch into space.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Destroy all Black Sun near the trinity base.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Return to Dartas to report your failure.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: You Failed Your Mission, Return to Dartas
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Report to Dartas of your success.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Land and Report back to Dartas
